'''祕魯巨人蜈蚣'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Scolopendra gigantea}}''）是[[世界|世界]]上最大的[[蜈蚣|蜈蚣]]。棲息於[[南美洲|南美洲]]與[[加勒比地區|加勒比地區]]，平均長度為{{convert|30|cm|in}}<ref name="cc">{{cite journal |author1=R. M. Shelley |author2=S. B. Kiser |lastauthoramp=yes |title=Neotype designation and a diagnostic account for the centipede, ''Scolopendra gigantea'' L. 1758, with an account of ''S. galapagoensis'' Bollman 1889 (Chilopoda Scolopendromorpha Scolopendridae) |journal=Tropical Zoology |year=2000 |volume=13 |issue=1 |pages=159–170 |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/254325271_Neotype_designation_and_a_diagnostic_account_for_the_centipede_Scolopendra_gigantea_L_1758_with_an_account_of_S_galapagoensis_Bollman_1889_Chilopoda_Scolopendromorpha_Scolopendridae |doi=10.1080/03946975.2000.10531129 |access-date=2018-12-21 |archive-date=2018-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221182621/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/254325271_Neotype_designation_and_a_diagnostic_account_for_the_centipede_Scolopendra_gigantea_L_1758_with_an_account_of_S_galapagoensis_Bollman_1889_Chilopoda_Scolopendromorpha_Scolopendridae |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有的個體甚至能長到{{convert|38|cm|in|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite journal |author=R. M. Shelley & S. B. Kiser |title=Neotype designation and a diagnostic account for the centipede, ''Scolopendra gigantea'' L. 1758, with an account of ''S. galapagoensis'' Bollman 1889 (Chilopoda Scolopendromorpha Scolopendridae) |journal=[[Tropical_Zoology|Tropical Zoology]] |year=2000 |volume=13 |issue=1 |pages=159–170| id=ISSN: 0394-6975}}</ref>。以[[節肢動物|節肢動物]]、[[兩棲類|兩棲類]]、[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]與[[爬蟲類|爬蟲類]]為食<ref name="centipedes">{{cite journal |author=A. Arends |author2=R. J. Márquez |title=Predation by giant centipedes, ''Scolopendra gigantea'', on three species of bats in a Venezuelan cave |journal=[[Caribbean_Journal_of_Science|Caribbean Journal of Science]] |volume=41 |issue=2 |year=2005 |pages=340–346 |url=http://caribjsci.org/aug05/41_340-346.pdf |access-date=2018-12-21 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019054742/http://caribjsci.org/aug05/41_340-346.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 棲息與分佈地區 ==
祕魯巨人蜈蚣分佈於[[南美洲|南美洲]]北方，曾經採集過的樣本地區包括[[阿魯巴|阿魯巴]]、[[古拉索|古拉索]]、[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]、[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]]（含[[瑪格麗塔島|瑪格麗塔島]]）與[[千里達島|千里達島]]<ref name="cc"/>。來自[[聖托馬斯島_(美屬維爾京群島)|聖托馬斯島]]、[[海地|海地]]、[[多明尼加|多明尼加]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]、[[宏都拉斯|宏都拉斯]]的樣本則認為是標籤錯誤或是意外入侵<ref name="cc"/>。

祕魯巨人蜈蚣棲息於熱帶與亞熱帶雨林以及熱帶季節乾旱林。

== 行為與食性 ==
祕魯巨人蜈蚣為[[肉食動物|肉食動物]]，以其他[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]（包括大型[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]、[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]、[[馬陸|馬陸]]、[[蠍子|蠍子]]，甚至是[[捕鳥蛛|捕鳥蛛]]）與其他小型脊椎動物為食，包括[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]、[[青蛙|青蛙]]（最大體長95mm）、[[蛇|蛇]]（最大體長25cm）、[[麻雀|麻雀]]大小的[[鳥類|鳥類]]、[[老鼠|老鼠]]、[[蝙蝠|蝙蝠]]<ref name="centipedes"/>。大型個體透過倒吊於洞穴天花板上捕捉飛過的蝙蝠<ref name="centipedes"/>

